      <h2 class="mb-4" style="color: white;">Need Quality Tools?</h2>
      <p class="lead mb-4" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);">Visit FushidaLanka Hardware for premium tools, materials, and expert advice. Same-day delivery available!</p>
      <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-sm-row gap-3 justify-content-center">
        <a href="/products" class="btn btn-light btn-lg">Shop Now</a>
